title: Jenni `JWoww` Farley marries beau Roger Mathews
text: Jenni `JWoww` Farley marries beau Roger Mathews Monday, 19 October 2015 (11 minutes ago) *Washington D.C., Oct. 19 (ANI): Jenni 'JWoww' Farley recently got hitched with her longtime love Roger Mathews in front of her family and friends.* Washington D.C., Oct. 19 (ANI): Jenni 'JWoww' Farley recently got hitched with her longtime love Roger Mathews in front of her family and friends. The newly married couple said in a statement that it was by far one of the best days of their lives outside Meilani being born and added that they feel blessed to have their daughter on their special day, reports E! Online. The 29-year-old TV personality was seen wearing a custom dress by Stephen Yearick on her big day. Farley previously wrote on her website, "Roger is my perfect man in every way and he is the best daddy to Meilani that I could ever ever ask for. He accepts me in every way and I am more in love with him than ever!" (ANI)
